-Welcome to my selling journal!-
Heres the way I work things out. I accept Paypal and prefer it, its safe for both of us and fast. I will however, consider well concealed cash at your own risk, money orders, or trades.
I use recycled bubble mailers sometimes, but I will go out and buy new ones. I make sure to pack everything in an orderly manner and include little goodies when I can. I ship out same week and delivery confirmation and insurance is available upon your request.
